en.title: FE Expands in Egypt!
en.content:
QP Wearer, Champion Squash Player,Low Wee Wern with FE stockiest, Mr. Waleed Eldebaby in Egypt.
Low Wee Wern was in Cairo as part of the Malaysian National Team for the Squash World Championships.
